01:12:11.618 --> 01:12:14.788
[sighing] I… I think that,
you know, the son…

01:12:15.456 --> 01:12:16.749
I… I feel bad for him.

01:12:17.291 --> 01:12:20.836
Yes, that's a definite. I feel bad
