01:12:20.919 --> 01:12:23.922
-The dog I feel bad for too.
-I think they're both being abused.

01:12:24.006 --> 01:12:26.467
Yeah. I feel that Anna Nicole…

01:12:26.550 --> 01:12:28.635
I know she keeps saying
