[man] Just one per person.

01:16:23.328 --> 01:16:25.539
Okay, one per person, guys.
One per person.

01:16:26.164 --> 01:16:27.416
[man 2] Anna.

01:16:27.499 --> 01:16:28.959
[indistinct chatter]

01:16:32.170 --> 01:16:34.590
[man] My name is Maurice Brighthaupt.

01:16:34.673 --> 01:16:36.508
People know me as Big Moe.

01:16:37.175 --> 01:16:40.637
And I was Anna Nicole Smith's bodyguard.

01:16:42.306 --> 01:16:45.225
In the beginning, I think she tested me

01:16:45.309 --> 01:16:47.894
to see if I was trustworthy
to be with her.

01:16:49.187 --> 01:16:52.608
