You think I'm beautiful?"

01:16:52.691 --> 01:16:56.111
"Would you like to, you know,
see where we can go with this?"

01:16:56.612 --> 01:16:58.572
And I looked at her
dead in the eye and said,

01:16:58.655 --> 01:17:01.908
"Right now, I really think of you
as a little sister."

01:17:02.576 --> 01:17:05.245
And she shed a little tear.
She said, "You know what?"

01:17:06.038 --> 01:17:07.456
"I'm so glad I met you."

01:17:08.582 --> 01:17:12.711
After about two days of working with her,
I started calling her baby girl.

01:17:12.794 --> 01:17:15.339
And from that point on,
she called me Momo.

01:17:15.422 --> 01:17:17.466
[reporter 1] Get back. Get back. Anna!

01:17:17.549 --> 01:17:19.301
[crowd clamoring]

01:17:20.052 --> 01:17:21.637
[reporter 2] Anna! Way over here!

01:17:21.720 --> 01:17:22.721
[reporter 3] Anna!

01:17:23.513 --> 01:17:26.099
[Maurice] She had to present Kanye West
with the award

01:17:26.183 --> 01:17:28.352
at the American Music Awards.

01:17:28.435 --> 01:17:32.939
And before she went on stage,
Howard and her was talking,

01:17:33.023 --> 01:17:36.818
and I said, "This is gonna be great.
You're gonna be on stage."

01:17:40.530 --> 01:17:41.531
"Be yourself."

01:17:42.157 --> 01:17:44.284
And that's when she sat back and thought,

01:17:45.369 --> 01:17:49.665
"Wow, I'm going to do something
that everyone will always remember."

01:17:50.207 --> 01:17:52.042
[announcer] Anna Nicole Smith.

01:17:52.125 --> 01:17:53.710
[crowd cheering, applauding]

01:17:53.794 --> 01:17:55.545
[show music playing]

01:17:56.338 --> 01:17:57.673
[Maurice] She got up on stage

01:17:57.756 --> 01:18:00.258
