01:18:35.544 --> 01:18:36.545
"How did I do?"

01:18:38.839 --> 01:18:41.425
Off the camera,
and we was all by ourselves,

01:18:41.508 --> 01:18:42.759
Anna was with it.

01:18:42.843 --> 01:18:44.761
-[reporters clamoring]
-[camera shutters clicking]

01:18:44.845 --> 01:18:45.887
[Maurice] And after that,

01:18:45.971 --> 01:18:49.307
we got so many other speaking engagements
to go to.

01:18:50.308 --> 01:18:52.018
[Anna] It's crazy.

01:18:52.644 --> 01:18:54.229
It's totally crazy.

01:18:54.312 --> 01:18:58.483
Everyone out of the blue is calling.
Calling, calling, calling.

01:18:58.567 --> 01:19:01.987
And I didn't even have to do a…
a sex tape.

01:19:02.070 --> 01:19:04.030
And I'm getting all this attention,

01:19:04.114 --> 01:19:06.158
and I'm like, "Oh my God."

01:19:06.908 --> 01:19:11.163
I'm like, "Wow!
