01:20:16.186 --> 01:20:17.729
[camera shutter clicking]

01:20:17.813 --> 01:20:19.981
And so as soon as
he met Anna Nicole Smith,

01:20:20.065 --> 01:20:21.650
the light bulb went off above his head,

01:20:21.733 --> 01:20:24.444
and he was like,
"Ooh, this could be quite lucrative."

