♪ Yes, my heart belongs to Daddy ♪

01:54:20.645 --> 01:54:24.607
♪ So I simply couldn't be bad ♪

01:54:25.275 --> 01:54:29.529
♪ Yes, my heart belongs to Daddy ♪

01:54:30.113 --> 01:54:34.075
♪ Da, da, da, da, da, da, da, da, dad ♪

01:54:34.784 --> 01:54:39.539
♪ So I want to warn you, laddie ♪

01:54:39.622 --> 01:54:43.418
♪ Though I know
That you're perfectly swell ♪

01:54:44.377 --> 01:54:48.631
♪ That my heart belongs to Daddy ♪

01:54:50.008 --> 01:54:52.135
♪ 'Cause my Daddy ♪

01:54:54.888 --> 01:55:00.518
♪ He treats it so ♪

01:55:00.602 --> 01:55:02.145
[song fades]

01:55:02.228 --> 01:55:04.230
[somber music playing]

01:56:28.731 --> 01:56:30.733
[music fades]
